et":"/static/7945ee2d0d6c01089eb11463e2bbf51d/93dd2/Image-6.4.21-PMG-Donation.webp 300w,\n/static/7945ee2d0d6c01089eb11463e2bbf51d/336f1/Image-6.4.21-PMG-Donation.webp 600w,\n/static/7945ee2d0d6c01089eb11463e2bbf51d/77a67/Image-6.4.21-PMG-Donation.webp 1200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px, 100vw"}]},"width":1200,"height":723}}}}}},{"categories":{"nodes":[{"name":"Agency News"}]},"title":"Beyer Boys Names The PM Group Agency of Record","slug":"beyer-boys-names-the-pm-group-agency-of-record","featuredImage":{"node":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/a63cb5f8cdcc839374380b6777b343ff/e4495/Image-Beyer-Boys-Blog.png","srcSet":"/static/a63cb5f8cdcc839374380b6777b343ff/5329f/Image-Beyer-Boys-Blog.png 300w,\n/static/a63cb5f8cdcc839374380b6777b343ff/6d090/Image-Beyer-Boys-Blog.png 600w,\n/static/a63cb5f8cdcc839374380b6777b343ff/e4495/Image-Beyer-Boys-Blog.png 1200w","sizes":"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/a63cb5f8cdcc839374380b6777b343ff/93dd2/Image-Beyer-Boys-Blog.webp 300w,\n/static/a63cb5f8cdcc839374380b6777b343ff/336f1/Image-Beyer-Boys-Blog.webp 600w,\n/static/a63cb5f8cdcc839374380b6777b343ff/77a67/Image-Beyer-Boys-Blog.webp 1200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px, 100vw"}]},"width":1200,"height":723}}}}}}]}}]}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDo2MzA5NA==","content":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><span class=\"wp-image-60380 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:52.734375%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/85b06/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/bc282/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/f1720/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/85b06/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/bc282/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/f1720/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/f1720/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/85b06/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/bc282/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/f1720/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/85b06/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/bc282/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/f1720/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/264349aa86a16c724cc89181a3466afa/f1720/Image-2.26.21-Beyer-1024x538.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>In the advertising agency world, it is always fun and effective to break the mold of traditional TV commercials. Whenever our clients are open to fun and creative new takes on classic, industry-standard themes, we jump into brainstorming mode. <a href=\"https://beyerplumbing.com/\"><strong>Beyer Plumbing</strong></a> wanted to do just that and spread the word about their latest services promotion. So, our creative team here at <strong><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\">The PM Group</a></strong> collaborated to create a sweet and furry way to share the news.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>Animal actors always have a way of tugging at our heartstrings and making us laugh. Remember that sweet yellow lab’s unlikely friendship with a Clydesdale in one of Budweiser’s most memorable <a href=\"https://youtu.be/otCxSnu_HXA\"><strong>Super Bowl ads</strong></a>? Or maybe Bridgestone’s hilarious <a href=\"https://youtu.be/NCrrnC8P1lk\"><strong>screaming squirrel commercial</strong></a>? So, when we weaved the commercial storyline of blaming the dog, or cat, or even a parrot for a leaking water heater mess in the house&#8211;we went for it!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>You can watch our latest commercial below and be sure to take advantage of Beyer Plumbing’s latest water heater installation discount. Beyer Plumbing has over 30 years of experience when it comes to any plumbing needs in your home &#8211; pet or human caused. We won’t point fingers.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n<div>\n<h2>Beyer Plumbing &#8220;Pets&#8221;</h2>\n<div id=\"schema-videoobject\" class=\"video-container\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Lp5KnwnMtU8?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0\" width=\"853\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 100px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 33 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profits, real estate and fitness. For two consecutive years now, the Agency has set annual revenue records with the addition of six new clients and through the continued success of our existing clients. Additionally, the agency hosts their annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In 2020 alone, the Agency donated over $1,050,000 to local non-profits. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"Beyer Plumbing Unveils New Commercial Featuring Furry Actors","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Beyer Plumbing Unveils New Commercial Featuring Furry Actors","url":"/beyer-plumbing-unveils-new-commercial-featuring-furry-actors/"}],"title":"Beyer Plumbing Unveils New Commercial Featuring Furry Actors | The PM Group","metaDesc":"When we had the chance with Beyer Plumbing to weave the storyline of blaming the dog, or cat, or even a parrot for a leaking water heater mess in the house--we went for it!","focuskw":"Beyer Plumbing","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Beyer Plumbing Unveils New Commercial Featuring Furry Actors | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"When we had the chance with Beyer Plumbing to weave the storyline of blaming the dog, or cat, or even a parrot for a leaking water heater mess in the house--we went for it!","opengraphImage":null,"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":{"altText":"Beyer Plumbing - The PM Group San Antonio Advertising Agency","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywhee